interactions.flavorLineOne: The irregularity in the Drifter's machine is mirroring a gravitational disturbance being emitted from the Cradle. It has attracted attention from Savathûn's forces. Eris requests you clear a path to the Tree of Silver Wings.

"Gotta make sure that Seed's charged up for Eris's little phone calls to the Darkness; otherwise, all you're gonna hear is static and interference. No one likes that. Charge up, and keep bringing me that Umbral junk to tune up my tech. We'll be kickin' right along in no time, like a can down the road." —The Drifter
